title: The Invisible Seam: Unsung Stories of Black Culture and Fashion with Kimberly Jenkins
itunes:title: The Invisible Seam: Unsung Stories of Black Culture and Fashion with Kimberly Jenkins
description:
Kimberly Jenkins joins us to discuss her new podcast The Invisible Seam: Unsung Stories of Black Culture and Fashion, in partnership with Tommy Hilfiger.
